# Redactions applied during skill build

Two passes ran:

1. **Regex/entropy scrub** of the raw recording before it was sent to Claude.
   Sensitive values are replaced with typed placeholders.
2. **Post-LLM secret check** over the rendered SKILL.md, run by Haiku 4.5 to
   catch anything the regex pass missed.

Review both lists before installing the skill.

